narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: This class covers a lot of vocabulary along with verbs and verb conjugations. We mostly learned about verb usage in the past and future tenses.
I learned how to read more complex texts, speak with a wider vocabulary, and be able to understand authentic commercials and websites.

narratives.question_text: What are the strengths and weaknesses of this course and how could it be improved?
comments:
Strength: A lot of material covered, opportunity to learn a lot.

Weakness: A lot of the work given for outside of class felt not very useful and more like busy work.
Very well taught course, with thoughtfully planned assignments and material. Nothing much to improve.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: I would - the class was enjoyable, just know that it will take up a good amount of your time. There will be a decent amount of work every night of the week.
